          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7471412-lorrea---whatchareadin?shelf=books-by-ipod">books-by-ipod</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7471412-lorrea---whatchareadin?shelf=kerry-hunter-in-memory">kerry-hunter-in-memory</a>, 
