op of the heap.  The novel chronicles the continuing investigations of Detectives Zach Jordan and Kylie MacDonald. Beginning shortly after the end of NYPD Red 2 with the beginning of a new year and a new mayoral tenure, the novel sees Jordan and MacDonald pursue the killer of a New York investment tycoon’s Haitian chauffer and run into a kidnapping that the tycoon desires to keep secret. Generational tensions and sordid financial dealings come to light throughout the novel, as well as romantic difficulties for both Jordan and MacDonald. Followers of the still-young series will not be disappointed in what they find in the novel.  This companion to NYPD Red 3 also includes the following: • Book Review • Story Setting Analysis of NYPD Red 3 • Story elements you may have missed as we decipher the novel • Details of Characters &amp; Key Character Analysis • Summary of the text, with some analytical comments interspersed • Thought Provoking /or Discussion Questions for both Readers &amp; Book Clubs • Discussion &amp; Analysis of Themes, Symbols… • And Much More!  This Analysis of NYPD Red 3 fills the gap, making you understand more while enhancing your reading experience.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"5266505554789271390\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'18_book_25178710\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"ZO2+/m1D2kRW9Qb+GksyycF7W+VC+l+fm609TSKFqBLyxYyK97OrjS16uMiZjVlF6zaaEz7SPe1XhvTf1y3Rmw==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"25178710\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"18_book_25178710\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr